short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Toggle between light and dark mode on Zendesk. Extension by Tomasz Nowicki.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Zendesk Dark Mode is a user-friendly plugin designed to enhance your Zendesk experience by allowing you to switch effortlessly between light and dark themes. This plugin is perfect for those who prefer a darker interface, which can help reduce eye strain and improve focus, especially during extended periods of use.

Tip:  After installing this extension make sure that you have refreshed Zendesk page.
